description: "This map of the island of Billiton (Belitung, Indonesia) features mountains, rivers, railways, roads, settlements, coconut plantations and administrative borders. An inset map shows the island’s port and capital city Tanjung Pandan."
title: "Topographische   kaart   van   het   eiland   Billiton   :   vluchtig   opgenomen   in   de   jaren   1877-1878"
